WEBVTT

00:01.833 --> 00:02.759
Who are you?

00:02.760 --> 00:04.226
Let's just say I'm someone

00:04.227 --> 00:05.526
who's chosen to embrace
the full spectrum

00:05.528 --> 00:07.195
of our reality.

00:08.425 --> 00:10.644
Um, FBI's
at the front gate.

00:10.646 --> 00:12.942
Will! Abby... Corrigan?

00:12.943 --> 00:14.739
I think it's going quite well.

00:14.741 --> 00:16.642
When I first
knew you at Oxford,

00:16.644 --> 00:18.340
I loved you
with my entire being.

00:20.912 --> 00:22.375
You destroyed my heart, John,

00:22.377 --> 00:24.811
the hatred you feel
towards me...

00:24.813 --> 00:27.678
Then the way you would
harm our daughter.

00:27.680 --> 00:29.513
Fair warning, Dr. Zimmerman,

00:29.515 --> 00:31.816
you're about to leave
the world you know behind.

00:31.818 --> 00:33.285
I'm a psychologist.

00:33.287 --> 00:34.853
You work with monsters.

00:34.855 --> 00:36.957
But I can promise you
the adventure

00:36.959 --> 00:38.897
of many,
many lifetimes.

00:40.267 --> 00:41.834
Shall we begin?

00:43.000 --> 00:49.074
