contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:50.951 --> 00:52.853
Hey! Hey, wait!

00:52.855 --> 00:53.921
Wait!

00:53.923 --> 00:56.593
Aw, come on!

00:56.595 --> 00:59.232
It's not even 8:00 yet!

00:59.234 --> 01:00.800
Did you
catch them?

01:00.802 --> 01:03.405
No, and I don't think
last week's salmon

01:03.407 --> 01:04.973
wants to stay
with us either.

01:04.974 --> 01:08.243
Oh, wonderful.

01:08.245 --> 01:09.878
Roy, I hope you
get your timing

01:09.880 --> 01:12.248
from your mother,
and not me.

01:13.250 --> 01:16.319
We are not naming
our daughter "Roy."

01:16.321 --> 01:19.890
Yes, we are, if <i> he</i> is going
to be a major leaguer.

01:19.892 --> 01:21.459
There's a Cy Young
award-winner in there,

01:21.461 --> 01:23.494
I can feel it.

01:24.497 --> 01:26.898
Surgery can't start
without you.

01:28.267 --> 01:29.868
Go be brilliant.

01:29.870 --> 01:32.404
You put your feet up
and eat bon-bons, okay?

01:32.406 --> 01:34.039
I have prenatal yoga

01:34.041 --> 01:35.641
in an hour.

01:35.643 --> 01:37.744
Chocolate.
Roy wants chocolate.

01:40.549 --> 01:41.883
Love you.

01:41.885 --> 01:44.452
Love you.

01:45.522 --> 01:47.456
Oh, you gotta be kidding me.

01:52.064 --> 01:53.564
Come here.

01:53.566 --> 01:55.466
Come here.

01:56.403 --> 01:57.903
Come here.

01:57.905 --> 01:59.905
Come here...

01:59.907 --> 02:01.307
Come here, come here.

02:05.380 --> 02:06.546
Okay...

02:11.318 --> 02:12.985
Just... just relax.

02:30.803 --> 02:33.740
On the trunk of my car.

02:33.742 --> 02:34.707
Again.

02:34.709 --> 02:35.742
Come here,
Henry, darling.

02:36.945 --> 02:38.979
You all right?

02:38.981 --> 02:40.848
I've got him.

02:40.850 --> 02:43.084
You know, you might want
to think about declawing him

02:43.086 --> 02:44.986
before he scratches
the paint on my Beemer,

02:44.988 --> 02:47.523
or maybe just don't
let him out so much.

02:47.525 --> 02:49.626
"Declaw"?

02:49.628 --> 02:50.527
He's an innocent creature.

02:50.529 --> 02:52.462
Unlike your dog,

02:52.464 --> 02:55.766
who keeps doing his
business on my lawn.

02:55.768 --> 02:57.435
Monty?

02:57.437 --> 02:59.037
No, that's not possible.
We have a dog-walker.

02:59.039 --> 03:01.407
Keep him on your side
of the street.

03:02.709 --> 03:03.609
What the hell is that?

03:03.611 --> 03:05.411
Oi!

03:10.418 --> 03:11.552
Are you quite through?

03:12.821 --> 03:16.457
Uh... I'm sorry, I just
thought I saw something.

03:16.459 --> 03:18.393
When I want you
in my house, Dr. Zimmerman,

03:18.395 --> 03:20.128
I will invite you into my house.

03:20.130 --> 03:23.099
Don't expect that invitation
anytime soon!

03:23.101 --> 03:24.734
Get out!

03:24.736 --> 03:26.168
Right.

03:26.170 --> 03:29.172
Sorry. I just...

03:33.802 --> 03:37.802
<font color=#00FF00>♪ Sanctuary 3x19 ♪</font>
<font color=#00FFFF>Out of the Blue</font>
